node.text:
These days, you don't need to own a sewing machine to tailor elements of your space. @jojotastic shares how she easily customized curtains at home for her new gear room:

"I’m very intimidated by sewing, so instead I used iron-on hem adhesive from @amazonhome to perfectly tailor each panel to our windows. I absolutely love how they turned out—especially that pop of plaid! Nothing quite says ‘cabin’ like plaid, don’t you think?"

Interested in recreating this fun DIY curtain look or finding tools to organize your hobby closet? Tap the link in our bio to shop it all! #amazonhome #founditonamazon
